title: Zocalo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Modern, quick service chain Mexican food restaurant. Offers a separate vegetarian menu with a range of items mirroring the non-veg items. Many of the veg items can be made vegan - specify no cheese, etc. In addition to beans and rice, veggie strips and pulled jackfruit are offered as filling for burritos, tacos, quesadillas. Has menu in English.
